      "content": "it's just a bit of a dull ringing too. honestly i've had ringing in my ears before and it's usually fine once it settles. do you think maybe i just pushed some wax deeper with the cotton swab? i could probably just try some ear drops or something tomorrow morning and wait it out if i don't do anything tonight. seems like an overkill to go to the hospital for just a clogged feeling.",
